Package innovent.birt.functions

Each class in this package represents a ScriptFunction extension.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
AppendLibraryContent Utility function that will add a ReportItem from a library into your report.
BindParameters Edits all the data sets in the report.
BirtLogger Arguments: message (String) - the message to log priority (String) - one of "ALL", "FINE", "FINER", "FINEST", "INFO", "SEVERE", "WARNING", or "OFF"
DisplayParameters Utility method that will insert a grid at the head of your report displaying the values of the parameters that the user passed to the report.

ThrowException Throws an error that will show up in the report design and be accessible from the runTask.getErrors() method Arguments: Message ReportContext [optional] If the reportContext is not supplied, then an Unhandled JavaScript exception will be thrown.
 

Package innovent.birt.functions Description

Each class in this package represents a ScriptFunction extension. The name of the class should match the name of the function as defined in the plugin.xml file.
